headline: Omnicom (OMC) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Omnicom (OMC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 3.88% and 0.70%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
